  <div class="container">
  <!-- Services Overview -->
  <section class="services-overview">
  <h2>Comprehensive Economic Analysis Services Across the United States</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">Skerritt Economics & Consulting provides expert forensic economics and business valuation services to attorneys, businesses, and government agencies throughout all 50 states and Washington DC. Our team delivers consistent, court-tested methodologies with nationwide expertise.</p>

  <div class="services-grid">
  <div class="service-card">
  <span class="benefit-icon"><i class="icon icon-forensic-economics icon-xl" aria-label="Forensic Economics"></i></span>
  <h3>Forensic Economics</h3>
  <p>Economic damage calculations for personal injury, wrongful death, and employment litigation. Lost earnings projections, life care cost analysis, and present value determinations.</p>
  <a href="/services/forensic-economics/" class="learn-more">Learn More →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
  <span class="benefit-icon"><i class="icon icon-business-valuation icon-xl" aria-label="Business Valuation"></i></span>
  <h3>Business Valuation</h3>
  <p>Expert business valuations for litigation support, divorce proceedings, shareholder disputes, and estate planning. Fair market value assessments meeting court standards.</p>
  <a href="/services/business-valuation/" class="learn-more">Learn More →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
  <span class="benefit-icon">💼</span>
  <h3>Vocational Assessment</h3>
  <p>Comprehensive earning capacity evaluations, vocational rehabilitation planning, and transferable skills analysis for disability and personal injury cases.</p>
  <a href="/services/#vocational-assessment" class="learn-more">Learn More →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
  <span class="benefit-icon"><i class="icon icon-life-care icon-xl" aria-label="Life Care Planning"></i></span>
  <h3>Life Care Planning</h3>
  <p>Certified life care planning services providing detailed future medical care cost projections for catastrophic injury cases. Medicare Set-Aside allocations available.</p>
  <a href="/services/#life-care-planning" class="learn-more">Learn More →</a>
  </div>
  </div>
  </section>

